setCombatMode 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Set group combat mode (engagement rules).Mode may be one of:  "BLUE 
" (Never fire) "GREEN" (Hold fire - defend only) "WHITE" (Hold fire 
, engage at will) "YELLOW" (Fire at will) "RED" (Fire at will, engage 
 at will) 
Syntax:  
 groupName setCombatMode mode 
Parameters: 
groupName: Object or Group 
mode: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing